  <qti-item-body>
    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices="1" response-identifier="RESPONSE">
      <qti-prompt data-catalog-idref="tts_prompt">
        <p>Where is the climax in Freytag's Pyramid?</p>
      </qti-prompt>
      <qti-simple-choice fixed="true" identifier="A">
        <div data-catalog-idref="tts_choice_A">
          <p>At the very beginning, before the action starts</p>
        </div>
        <qti-feedback-block identifier="feedback_A" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK" show-hide="show">
          <qti-content-body>
            <div class="tb-feedback-incorrect" data-catalog-idref="feedback_A">
              <p>The very beginning is the exposition — the setup before anything's gone wrong. The climax comes much later.</p>
            </div>
          </qti-content-body>
        </qti-feedback-block>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice fixed="true" identifier="B">
        <div data-catalog-idref="tts_choice_B">
          <p>At the top — the peak of the pyramid</p>
        </div>
        <qti-feedback-block identifier="feedback_B" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK" show-hide="show">
          <qti-content-body>
            <div class="tb-feedback-correct" data-catalog-idref="feedback_B">
              <p>Correct! The climax is the peak of the pyramid — the turning point everything pivots on, with rising action climbing toward it and falling action rippling out after.</p>
            </div>
          </qti-content-body>
        </qti-feedback-block>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice fixed="true" identifier="C">
        <div data-catalog-idref="tts_choice_C">
          <p>At the end, where things settle down</p>
        </div>
        <qti-feedback-block identifier="feedback_C" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK" show-hide="show">
          <qti-content-body>
            <div class="tb-feedback-incorrect" data-catalog-idref="feedback_C">
              <p>The end is the resolution, where things settle and the loose ends get tied — by then the turning point has already passed.</p>
            </div>
          </qti-content-body>
        </qti-feedback-block>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice fixed="true" identifier="D">
        <div data-catalog-idref="tts_choice_D">
          <p>Outside the pyramid entirely</p>
        </div>
        <qti-feedback-block identifier="feedback_D" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK" show-hide="show">
          <qti-content-body>
            <div class="tb-feedback-incorrect" data-catalog-idref="feedback_D">
              <p>Every stage of the story, climax included, lives on the pyramid — that's the whole point of the shape.</p>
            </div>
          </qti-content-body>
        </qti-feedback-block>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
